title: Kulap Vilaysack
description: Kulap Vilaysack (Who Charted?, comedy!) is a true delight. Fun, funny, thoughtful: just the ideal guest. Pete and K had a blast, we hope you do too! Now you know what to do: Get. Into. It. Weirdos!!
